          <ul class="m-0" style="list-style-type:'–&nbsp;&nbsp;';padding-left:1em;">
            <li>Scaling order fulfillment through a vast on-demand third party delivery network</li>
            <li>Automated parcel sorting and pushing to accurately push parcels on the road in minimal time</li>
            <li>Enabling customers to have more control over deliveries with preferred delivery windows and options</li>
            <li>Being customers’ preferred choice with seamless reverse logistics optimized through route planning solutions</li>
          </ul>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

